HARASSMENT POLICY

Harassment includes repeated unwanted contact, slurs, sexual harassment,
threats, or targeting a player after being asked to stop.

What to do:
  1. Use ignore or block features if available.
  2. Do not escalate in public channels.
  3. Report the incident: help reporting
  4. Staff will review logs when possible.

False reports made in bad faith may themselves result in action.

